#nmap scan port
#Scan for all devices and open ports on a local network:
%nmap -sP 192.168.1.0/24
#Scan a website for open ports:
%nmap www.example.com
#Detect OS and Services. This will attempt OS detection, version detection, script scanning, and traceroute.
%nmap -A 192.168.1.10

